statements: SELECT * FROM team_performance
SELECT team_name, performance_score FROM team_performance WHERE performance_score > 80
SELECT team_id, team_name FROM team_performance ORDER BY team_name ASC
SELECT team_leader, engagement_score FROM team_performance WHERE engagement_score < 60
SELECT AVG(performance_score) AS avg_performance FROM team_performance
SELECT team_name, team_leader, performance_score FROM team_performance WHERE performance_score > 80 ORDER BY team_name ASC
SELECT team_name, engagement_score FROM team_performance WHERE engagement_score BETWEEN 60 AND 80 ORDER BY engagement_score DESC
SELECT team_name, team_leader FROM team_performance WHERE team_id IN (1, 3, 5) ORDER BY team_leader ASC
SELECT team_name, performance_score FROM team_performance WHERE performance_score < 70 ORDER BY performance_score DESC
SELECT * FROM team_performance WHERE team_leader IN ('John Doe', 'Jane Smith')
SELECT * FROM virtual_team_leaders;
SELECT name, performance_score FROM virtual_team_leaders WHERE id = 1;
SELECT team_lead_id, COUNT(team_id) AS total_teams FROM team_performance GROUP BY team_lead_id HAVING COUNT(team_id) > 1;
SELECT * FROM team_performance WHERE project_id = 1234 ORDER BY performance_rating DESC;
SELECT name, performance_rating FROM virtual_team_leaders INNER JOIN team_performance ON virtual_team_leaders.team_lead_id = team_performance.team_lead_id WHERE team_id = 5;
SELECT id, name, performance_score FROM virtual_team_leaders WHERE performance_score > 90 ORDER BY name DESC;
SELECT team_lead_id, team_id, project_id, performance_rating FROM team_performance WHERE performance_rating >= 8 ORDER BY team_id, project_id;
SELECT id, name, performance_score FROM virtual_team_leaders WHERE name LIKE 'J%' OR name LIKE 'S%' ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT team_lead_id, AVG(performance_rating) AS avg_rating FROM team_performance GROUP BY team_lead_id HAVING avg_rating > 7 ORDER BY avg_rating DESC;
SELECT id, name, performance_score FROM virtual_team_leaders WHERE id IN (1, 3, 5) ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT * FROM team_members;
SELECT member_name, joining_date FROM team_members WHERE performance_rating > 8;
SELECT member_name, performance_rating FROM team_members ORDER BY performance_rating DESC;
SELECT team_id, COUNT(member_id) AS total_members FROM team_members GROUP BY team_id;
SELECT team_id, AVG(performance_rating) AS avg_rating FROM team_members GROUP BY team_id;
SELECT member_name, performance_rating FROM team_members ORDER BY performance_rating DESC;
SELECT team_id, AVG(efficiency_score) AS avg_efficiency_score FROM team_scores GROUP BY team_id;
SELECT team_id, COUNT(*) AS member_count FROM team_members GROUP BY team_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5;
SELECT t.team_id, t.analysis_date, ta.performance_insights FROM team_scores t JOIN team_analysis ta ON t.team_id = ta.team_id WHERE t.efficiency_score > 80;
SELECT member_name, joining_date, engagement_score FROM team_members tm JOIN team_scores ts ON tm.member_id = ts.member_id WHERE ts.engagement_score < 50 ORDER BY joining_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM virtual_team_leaders;
SELECT team_name, team_size FROM virtual_team_leaders ORDER BY team_name DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT location FROM virtual_team_leaders;
SELECT team_leader_id, team_size, location FROM virtual_team_leaders WHERE team_size > 5;
SELECT team_name, team_size, location FROM virtual_team_leaders WHERE team_size < 10 ORDER BY team_size ASC;
SELECT team_name, team_size FROM virtual_team_leaders WHERE team_size > 10 ORDER BY team_name DESC;

SELECT team_name, location FROM virtual_team_leaders INNER JOIN team_performance ON virtual_team_leaders.team_leader_id = team_performance.team_leader_id WHERE team_performance.performance_score > 8 ORDER BY team_performance.date ASC;
SELECT AVG(engagement_score) AS average_engagement, COUNT(*) AS total_engagements FROM team_engagement GROUP BY team_leader_id HAVING total_engagements > 3 ORDER BY average_engagement DESC;
SELECT team_leader_id, team_name, location FROM virtual_team_leaders WHERE location LIKE '%New York%' ORDER BY team_leader_id ASC;

SELECT team_name, COUNT(*) AS no_of_members FROM virtual_team_leaders LEFT JOIN team_members ON virtual_team_leaders.team_leader_id = team_members.team_leader_id GROUP BY team_name HAVING no_of_members < 5 ORDER BY no_of_members DESC;
SELECT * FROM VirtualTeamLeaders;
SELECT leader_id, leader_name, team_id FROM VirtualTeamLeaders WHERE team_id = 10;
SELECT team_name, leader_name, join_date FROM VirtualTeamLeaders ORDER BY join_date DESC;
SELECT performance_id, team_id, performance_score FROM TeamPerformance WHERE performance_score > 80;
SELECT task_name, team_id, completion_status FROM TeamTasks WHERE team_id = 5 ORDER BY task_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM VirtualTeamLeaders WHERE team_id = 101;
SELECT team_id, team_name FROM VirtualTeamLeaders WHERE leader_name = 'John Doe' ORDER BY join_date DESC;
SELECT leader_name, team_name, join_date FROM VirtualTeamLeaders WHERE leader_id IN (3, 6, 9);
SELECT task_name, task_description, completion_status FROM TeamTasks WHERE team_id = 201 AND completion_status = TRUE;
SELECT member_name, join_date FROM TeamMembers WHERE team_id = 301 ORDER BY join_date ASC;
